  "stem": "<p>Let the function <i>q</i> be defined as <i>q</i>(<i>x</i>) = ((<i>x</i> &minus; <i>c</i>)&sup2; + 80)/(2<i>c</i>), where <i>c</i> is a constant. If <i>q</i>(<i>c</i>) = 10, what is the value of <i>q</i>(12)?</p>",
