  "rationale": "<p>Choice D is correct. <i>q</i>(<i>c</i>) = (0 + 80)/(2<i>c</i>) = 40/<i>c</i> = 10, so <i>c</i> = 4. Then <i>q</i>(12) = ((12 &minus; 4)&sup2; + 80)/(8) = (64 + 80)/8 = 144/8 = 18.</p>",
